lgp.core.environment.constants

Interface ConstantLoader<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the constants.
    All Superinterfaces:
    ComponentLoader<TComponent>, Module
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DoubleConstantLoader, GenericConstantLoader

    public ConstantLoader<T>
extends ComponentLoader<TComponent>

    An extended interface ComponentLoader that loads a collection of values of type T to be used as constants.

    The implementer of this interface has control over all aspects of the loading process, all that is required is that when the inherited ComponentLoader.load method is called a collection of values of the correct type is given.

    Constants could be loaded by parsing some values defined in a configuration file, loaded from some database, or even hardcoded.

    See Also:
    interface ComponentLoader, ComponentLoader.load
